BEGIN
DECLARE @AlertMinTime datetime; DECLARE @AlertMaxTime datetime; DECLARE @Interval int; DECLARE @CurntInterval int; DECLARE @Count int; DECLARE @GatewayID varchar(100); DECLARE @BeaconID varchar(100); DECLARE @ShipmentID varchar(100); DECLARE @ShipmasterID int; DECLARE @GatewayStatus varchar(100); DECLARE @BeaconTmpProcess Table ( [BeaconID] varchar(100) ,[GatewayID] varchar(100) ,[Processed] tinyint
); INSERT INTO @BeaconTmpProcess SELECT DISTINCT r.[BeaconID],r.[GatewayID],0 from [Raw_Alert] r INNER JOIN [dbo].[Beacon_Object_Info] b ON r.[BeaconID]=b.[BeaconID] INNER JOIN [dbo].[Shipping_Master] sh ON b.[ShipMasterId]=sh.[ShipmasterID] WHERE r.[Status] = 'Raw' and sh.[IsActive] =1 and [ShipmentStatus] !='Closed' order by r.[BeaconID] --select * from @BeaconTmpProcess -----Process WHILE (SELECT Count(*) From @BeaconTmpProcess Where Processed = 0 ) > 0 BEGIN -----Loop Starts
SELECT TOP 1 @BeaconID = BeaconID ,@GatewayID = GatewayID FROM @BeaconTmpProcess Where Processed = 0 SELECT TOP 1 @AlertMinTime=[CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] FROM [dbo].[Raw_Alert] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status] = 'Raw' order by [CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] ASC --select @AlertMinTime SELECT TOP 1 @AlertMaxTime=[CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] FROM [dbo].[Raw_Alert] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status] = 'Raw' order by [CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] DESC --select @GatewayID set @ShipmentID=Null; set @ShipmasterID=0; Select distinct @ShipmasterID=ShipmasterID,@ShipmentID=ShipmentID from [dbo].[VW_Gateway_Pallet_ShipmentAssociation] where MacId=@GatewayID --select 'shipid'+@ShipmentID --select @ShipmasterID; SELECT @Interval= DATEDIFF(minute, @AlertMinTime, @AlertMaxTime); SELECT @CurntInterval= DATEDIFF(minute, @AlertMaxTime, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
IF (@ShipmasterID > 0 ) -- Valid Shipmaster Id BEGIN --Valid Shipmaster Check -- SELECT @Interval,@CurntInterval IF (@Interval >1 and @CurntInterval <10) Begin --select 'In Alert' if ((select count(BeaconID) from [dbo].[Alert_Process] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status]='Active')=0) Begin --select 'Alert-if not exists as status active then insert' INSERT INTO [dbo].[Alert_Process]([ShipmentID],[GatewayID] ,[BeaconID],[Temperature],[Humidity],[AlertType],[LocationLattitude],[LocationLongitude] ,[Acknowledge] ,[Ack_Notes],[User],[Status],[TimeStamp],[ShipmasterID],[AlertStartTime],[TemperatureAlert],[ShockAlert],[HumidityAlert],[TamperAlert]) Select Top 1 sh.ShipmentID,r.[GatewayID],r.[BeaconID],r.[Temperature],r.[Humidity],'Alert',r.[LocationLattitude],r.[LocationLongitude], '','','Job','Active',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,sh.[ShipmasterID],@AlertMinTime,r.[TemperatureAlert],r.[ShockAlert],r.[HumidityAlert],r.[TamperAlert] FROM [dbo].[Raw_Alert] r INNER JOIN [dbo].[Beacon_Object_Info] b ON r.[BeaconID]=b.[BeaconID] INNER JOIN [dbo].[Shipping_Master] sh ON b.[ShipMasterId]=sh.[ShipmasterID] WHERE r.[BeaconID]=@BeaconID and r.[Status] = 'Raw' AND [ShipmentStatus] !='Closed' and sh.[IsActive] =1 order by r.[CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] ASC
--Handling Null DELETE FROM [Alert_Process] WHERE ShipmentId is Null end --End Count Condition End --End Interval Condition Else Begin SELECT @GatewayStatus=d.[status] FROM [DeviceInfo] d WHERE d.MacId=@GatewayID if (@GatewayStatus ='Online') Begin ---select 'In non-Alert' if ((select count(BeaconID) from [dbo].[Alert_Process] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status]='Active')=1) Begin ---select 'NonAlert -if exists as status not closed then update as closed' Update [Alert_Process] set [AlertEndTime]=@AlertMaxTime, [Status]='Closed' where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [GatewayID]=@GatewayID and [Status]='Active' Update [Raw_Alert] set [Status] = 'Processed' where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [GatewayID]=@GatewayID and [Status] = 'Raw' End --End Count Condition End --GatewayStatus Condition End --End Else Interval Condition END -----Valid Shipmaster Check Ends UPDATE @BeaconTmpProcess Set Processed = 1 Where BeaconID=@BeaconID --Set Processed = 1 END -----Loop Ends
END --- SP ENd

BEGIN
DECLARE @AlertMinTime datetime; DECLARE @AlertMaxTime datetime; DECLARE @Interval int; DECLARE @CurntInterval int; DECLARE @Count int; DECLARE @GatewayID varchar(100); DECLARE @BeaconID varchar(100); DECLARE @ShipmentID varchar(100); DECLARE @ShipmasterID int; DECLARE @TamperAlert bit;
DECLARE @BeaconTmpProcess Table ( [BeaconID] varchar(100) ,[GatewayID] varchar(100) ,[Processed] tinyint
); INSERT INTO @BeaconTmpProcess SELECT DISTINCT [BeaconID],[GatewayID],0 from [Raw_Alert] WHERE [Status] = 'Raw' select * from @BeaconTmpProcess -----Process WHILE (SELECT Count(*) From @BeaconTmpProcess Where Processed = 0 ) > 0 BEGIN -----Loop Starts SET @TamperAlert=0; SELECT TOP 1 @BeaconID = BeaconID ,@GatewayID = GatewayID FROM @BeaconTmpProcess Where Processed = 0 SELECT TOP 1 @AlertMinTime=[CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] , @TamperAlert=[TamperAlert] FROM [dbo].[Raw_Alert] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status] = 'Raw' order by [CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] ASC --select @AlertMinTime SELECT TOP 1 @AlertMaxTime=[CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] FROM [dbo].[Raw_Alert] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status] = 'Raw' order by [CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] DESC ---select @AlertMaxTime Select distinct @ShipmasterID=ShipmasterID,@ShipmentID=ShipmentID from [dbo].[VW_Gateway_Pallet_ShipmentAssociation] where MacId=@GatewayID
SELECT @Interval= DATEDIFF(minute, @AlertMinTime, @AlertMaxTime); SELECT @CurntInterval= DATEDIFF(minute, @AlertMaxTime, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
SELECT @Interval,@CurntInterval,@AlertMinTime,@AlertMaxTime,@TamperAlert ------------------Tamper Alert Start------------ IF (@TamperAlert =1) Begin if ((select count(BeaconID) from [dbo].[Alert_Process] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status]='Active' and TamperAlert =1 )=0) Begin --select 'Alert-if not exists as status active then insert' INSERT INTO [dbo].[Alert_Process]([ShipmentID],[GatewayID] ,[BeaconID],[Temperature],[Humidity],[AlertType],[LocationLattitude],[LocationLongitude] ,[Acknowledge] ,[Ack_Notes],[User],[Status],[TimeStamp],[ShipmasterID],[AlertStartTime],[TemperatureAlert],[ShockAlert],[HumidityAlert],[TamperAlert]) Select Top 1 @ShipmentID,[GatewayID],[BeaconID],[Temperature],[Humidity],'Alert',[LocationLattitude],[LocationLongitude],'','','Job','Active',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,@ShipmasterID,@AlertMinTime,[TemperatureAlert],[ShockAlert],[HumidityAlert],[TamperAlert] FROM [dbo].[Raw_Alert] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status] = 'Raw' and TamperAlert =1 order by [CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] ASC
--Handling Null DELETE FROM [Alert_Process] WHERE ShipmentId is Null end --End Count Condition
End ------Tamper Alert End----------------- IF (@Interval >1 and @CurntInterval <10 and @TamperAlert =0) Begin select 'In Alert' if ((select count(BeaconID) from [dbo].[Alert_Process] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status]='Active')=0) Begin --select 'Alert-if not exists as status active then insert' INSERT INTO [dbo].[Alert_Process]([ShipmentID],[GatewayID] ,[BeaconID],[Temperature],[Humidity],[AlertType],[LocationLattitude],[LocationLongitude] ,[Acknowledge] ,[Ack_Notes],[User],[Status],[TimeStamp],[ShipmasterID],[AlertStartTime],[TemperatureAlert],[ShockAlert],[HumidityAlert],[TamperAlert]) Select Top 1 @ShipmentID,[GatewayID],[BeaconID],[Temperature],[Humidity],'Alert',[LocationLattitude],[LocationLongitude],'','','Job','Active',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,@ShipmasterID,@AlertMinTime,[TemperatureAlert],[ShockAlert],[HumidityAlert],[TamperAlert] FROM [dbo].[Raw_Alert] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status] = 'Raw' and TamperAlert =0 order by [CURRENTSYSTEMTIME] ASC
--Handling Null DELETE FROM [Alert_Process] WHERE ShipmentId is Null end --End Count Condition End --End Interval Condition Else Begin ---select 'In non-Alert' if ((select count(BeaconID) from [dbo].[Alert_Process] where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [Status]='Active' and TamperAlert =0 )=1) Begin ---select 'NonAlert -if exists as status not closed then update as closed' Update [Alert_Process] set [AlertEndTime]=@AlertMaxTime, [Status]='Closed' where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [GatewayID]=@GatewayID and [Status]='Active' Update [Raw_Alert] set [Status] = 'Processed' where [BeaconID]=@BeaconID and [GatewayID]=@GatewayID and [Status] = 'Raw' End --End Count Condition End --End Else Interval Condition
UPDATE @BeaconTmpProcess Set Processed = 1 Where BeaconID=@BeaconID --Set Processed = 1 END -----Loop Ends
END --- SP ENd
